# Authors

This file lists the primary authors and significant contributors to the Hafnium project.

## Original Authors

- **Hafnium Platform Team** - Initial architecture and implementation

## Contributors

Contributors are recognized for their valuable contributions to the project. For a complete list of contributors, please see the GitHub contributors page.

---

## Contribution Recognition

This project follows the [All Contributors](https://allcontributors.org/) specification. Contributions of any kind are welcome and will be recognized.

Types of contributions include:
- Code
- Documentation
- Design
- Infrastructure
- Testing
- Security
- Translation
- Research

---

## Becoming a Contributor

To become a listed contributor:

1. Make a meaningful contribution to the project
2. Have your contribution accepted via pull request
3. Your name will be added to this file or the GitHub contributors page

For contribution guidelines, see [CONTRIBUTING.md](CONTRIBUTING.md).

---

*This document is maintained by the Hafnium Platform Team.*
